songs.title: Flowers
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Precious child, running wild
Singing songs for your sick flowers
[?], overtired
Wind away the hours

[Chorus]
On your own
You're alone
Now

[Verse 2]
Little gone, silent sound
Soldier in his tower
Raging down, you have won
You have all the power

[Chorus]
On your own
You're alone
Now
